node.text:
#ad Surviving on protein bars and beer!
Wanted to review and share with you guys some of my favorite @imbuilt flavors while enjoying a  Kuri-Kuro Dark Chestnut Ale by the brewery Miyazaki Hideji Beer.
Give Built Bar a follow on Instagram and use my discount code thegirlwithbeer for $5 OFF 10 bar sample box.

Happy International Beer Day!
Double tap if you can relate 😆 I like my beer and pizza 🍕 and 🏋🏻‍♀️ it’s all about balance. 

I miss hanging out with my beer friends! @isbeeracarb @thebeermama @susiembennett @nikkidrinkscraft @mikmaven @littlemariii @thirsty_samurai_piggy

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Melis| Beer•Barbells•Travel in Vancouver, British Columbia with @mondayswimwear, @moodyales, @beerselfie, @beerselfiesofcanada, and @beerselfies_r_hot. May be an image of 1 person, drink, outdoors and text that says 'FLAMINGOSE'.

node.text:
❄️ 👙 ☀️ 🍺 
Didn’t get to share this one earlier but hiking in a bikini in the snow heading to a frozen lake while sipping on Flamingose by @moodyales is a Vancouver summer highlight for sure. 

What have you been up to so far this summer? 

🍺 Flamingose @moodyales gose brewed with grapefruit peel, coriander, and pink Himalayan salt. 

It’s been a while since I’ve had a gose and this beer reminded me why I used to love it so much. You do really have to like grapefruit and tart beers to enjoy this one, but if you do it’s a nice refreshing beer. 

Looking forward to more summer beers!

node.text:
I may not live in the US 🇺🇸 anymore but I still consider today national Independent beer run day. 🏃‍♀️ 🍺 

 Support small and independent breweries by stocking up your fridge and cooler for whatever adventures you’re going on this weekend! 

Drinking @settlementbrewing No Shrinking Violet, a Pea Flower Saison. It’s been a while since I’ve had a saison and this did not disappoint. Besides the beautiful can art, the beer itself pours our a pretty light purple color with a spice-forward aroma of ginger & clove. 💜
